[49m[38;5;10m+    535[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ### Expected Results
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    536[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    537[0m:[38;5;10m[49m **Sample daily forecast payload for a 380-bed community hospital:**
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    538[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    539[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```json
